title: Carli Lloyd scores in 85th minute, US ties Brazil 1-1
text: Facebook Email Twitter Google+ LinkedIn Pinterest Carli Lloyd scores in 85th minute, US ties Brazil 1-1 SEATTLE (AP) - Carli Lloyd scored in the 85th minute and the World Cup champion United States women pulled out a 1-1 tie with Brazil on Wednesday Post to Facebook Carli Lloyd scores in 85th minute, US ties Brazil 1-1 SEATTLE (AP) - Carli Lloyd scored in the 85th minute and the World Cup champion United States women pulled out a 1-1 tie with Brazil on Wednesday  //www.king5.com/story/sports/2015/10/22/carli-lloyd-scores-in-85th-minute-us-ties-brazil-1-1/74373914/   Join the Conversation To   Carli Lloyd scores in 85th minute, US ties Brazil 1-1 Associated Press 11:32 p.m. PDT October 21, 2015 Oct 21, 2015; Seattle, WA, USA; United States midfielder Carli Lloyd (10) gets a hug from teammates forward Alex Morgan (left) and midfielder Megan Rapinoe (right) as defender Becky Sauerbrunn (far left) celebrates with midfielder Morgan Brian (14) after Lloyd scored the equalizer during the second half against Brazil at Century Link Field. At right is Brazil defender Fabiana (2).
